---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle + " | Lublio"}>
  <BoxMarkdown
    title="프랑스어 알파벳"
    subtitle="L'alphabet du français"
    language="fra"
  />

  <main>
    <section class="group-a0 fade_1">
      <h1>
        <span class="animated-underline-fra">프랑스어 알파벳</span>
      </h1>
      <TableHorizontal numberOfColumns="3" data={frenchAlphabet} />
    </section>

    <section class="group-a1 fade_1">
      <h2>
        <span class="animated-underline-fra">기초 러시아어 (A1)</span>
      </h2>
      <h3>현재 제작중에 있습니다 🏗️</h3>
    </section>

    <section class="group-a2 fade_1">
      <h2>
        <span class="animated-underline-fra">초급 러시아어 (A2)</span>
      </h2>
      <h3>현재 제작중에 있습니다 🏗️</h3>
    </section>

    <section class="group-b1 fade_1">
      <h2>
        <span class="animated-underline-fra">중급 러시아어 (B1)</span>
      </h2>
      <h3>현재 제작중에 있습니다 🏗️</h3>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  section {
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
